  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00001",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "秦琼上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00002",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "登州城困住了秦叔宝，游来游去好心焦。眼看那八月中秋到，并无亲朋把咱瞧。我好比明月浮云照，沙滩困住浪里蛟。三家店内有人到，史大奈贤弟把书捎。恨徐勣把俺书按了，全不念金炉把香烧。提起单通心好恼，无义之人不可交。程咬金你把心死了，全不念救你出狱牢。我为你定下苦肉计，我为你两腿扎钢刀。想罗成八弟他不到，不念结拜念姑表。姑表弟兄相交好，骨肉相连筋一条。我母年高妻年少，还有秦山小根苗。将身坐在马鞍鞒，又听有人闹吵吵。",
      "text_length": 204
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00003",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "程咬金、尤俊达同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00004",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "打打打！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00005",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "罗周上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00006",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "哪是主拿哪是客？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00007",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "尤俊达"
      ],
      "text": "我是主他是客。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00008",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "主人低头客人讲来。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00009",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "我本是贩牛汉，今晚住了他的店，要米无有米，要面无有面，我怎么不打这个忘八旦！",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00010",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "客人低头，主人讲话。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00011",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "尤俊达"
      ],
      "text": "他今住了我的店，讲的一位三钱银子一顿饭，吃了我的八十包子六十面，一个小钱也无有给，请王爷断一断。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00012",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "王爷心中有事，若是无事，重责一百皮鞭，还不下去！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00013",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "尤俊达"
      ],
      "text": "虎。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00014",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "豹。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00015",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "尤俊达、程咬金同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00016",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "二哥，方才过去那是什么人？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00017",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟不认识？稳坐雕鞍听愚兄道来！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00018",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟莫把来人问，青面红发似天神。要问此人名和姓，班鸠店内程咬金。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00019",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "徐勣"
      ],
      "text": "南京收了南京去，北京收了北京游。南北二京全不收，条河两岸度春秋。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00020",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "徐勣"
      ],
      "text": "大哥魏徵，二哥李靖，三弟茂公为母许愿，舍药三年，舍了二载，还有一春，用药这厢来。",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00021",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "来者敢是茂公？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00022",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "徐勣"
      ],
      "text": "怎么说，贤弟冒了风了？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00023",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "徐勣"
      ],
      "text": "三片生姜两段葱，一晚温汤用腹中，盖上被子出身汗，哪管你冒风不冒风！",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00024",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "你是徐勣？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00025",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "徐勣"
      ],
      "text": "怎么方才冒了风，你又得了食积？下马来，我与你号脉。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00026",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "下马去了。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00027",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "徐勣"
      ],
      "text": "明白了，上马去罢。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00028",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "有罪了。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00029",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "徐勣"
      ],
      "text": "这是狗皮膏药四张，前心一张，后心一张，左膀一张，右膀一张，这是大红丸，一付用在腹中，药往外发，膏药往里发，好似两军阵前，冲锋打仗一般，出一身冷汗，你这病就好了。",
      "text_length": 80
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00030",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "请问用何药引？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00031",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "徐勣"
      ],
      "text": "只顾与兄台讲话，把药引都忘记了。虎的心，豹的胆，虎豹二字牢牢紧记，请吓！",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00032",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "徐勣下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00033",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "二哥方才过去那是什么人？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00034",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟不认识？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00035",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "不认识。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00036",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "将马勒后，听愚兄道来！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00037",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "在大街不敢通名姓，物吞八卦阴阳能。袖儿里常拿三才打，梨阳县里徐茂公。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00038",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟你我游来游去，并无比艺，你我回去罢。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00039",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "请二哥观阵。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00040",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "甚么？",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00041",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "请二哥观阵。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00042",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "闻听说观阵心纳闷，十分精神少九分。我在这登州城里命该尽，想起了高堂老娘亲。哭一声老娘心难忍，我的娘吓！何人送进秦家坟？别听那绿林兄弟同来问，他说我秦家是绝门。催动黄骠往前进，那边来了卖马人。",
      "text_length": 95
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00043",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "罗成上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00044",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗成"
      ],
      "text": "卖马吓卖马！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00045",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "来者敢是罗成？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00046",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗成"
      ],
      "text": "一匹马未从讲价，就说成与不成。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00047",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "为兄是秦琼。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00048",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗成"
      ],
      "text": "你穷算你命苦，哪个周济你不成？我这马如同虎豹一般，虎豹二字，牢牢紧记，请！",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00049",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "罗成下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00050",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "一言未尽罗成到，倒叫豪杰喜眉梢。杨龄贼呀时衰了，八弟花枪命难逃。喜盈盈来催黄骠，再叫贤弟听根苗！",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00051",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟此为何阵？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00052",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "金锁八卦连环斗底大阵。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00053",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "哪门进？哪门出？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00054",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "生门进，休门出。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00055",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "为兄杀在昏迷之间，哪晓得生门、休门？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00056",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "为弟枪头之上，挂着三尺红罗，随罗而进随罗而出。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00057",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "愚兄马上多谢了。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00058",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "观此阵我把雄心退，用枪一指骂老贼！杏马旗插在青龙背，摆下八卦九重雷。营门外大炮摆几对，中营安下振天雷。众家兄弟阵前对，设谋定计拿老贼。低下头来想半悔，细思想朋友还要为。佐黄骠闯在紫金对，再叫贤弟听明白！",
      "text_length": 101
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00059",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟此为何桥？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00060",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "绝命桥。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00061",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "何为绝命桥？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00062",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "杨龄与二哥交战，胜过二哥则罢了，胜不过二哥，将桥梁拆断，把二哥活活淹死在内。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00063",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "你二哥一死倒也罢了，岂不害了看桥之人？杨龄贼吓！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00064",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "观此阵把我的胆唬破，上是桥来下是河。你二哥一死还罢了，苦了看桥小哥哥！",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00065",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟此为何炮？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00066",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "振中胆。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00067",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "何为振中胆？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00068",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "罗周"
      ],
      "text": "杨龄与二哥交战，胜不过二哥，将此炮点着，把二哥活活振死在内。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005026_e00069",
      "play_id": "02005026",
      "scene_id": "02005026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
